  "response": "Whether porn stars enjoy double penetration, or any specific sexual activity, varies from individual to individual. Just like anyone else, adult performers have their own personal preferences, boundaries, and comfort levels when it comes to sexual activities. \n\nIn the adult entertainment industry, scenes are typically negotiated and agreed upon in advance between performers and production teams. This means that the activities depicted are consensual and based on what the performers have agreed to participate in. However, agreeing to perform a particular act for a scene doesn't necessarily mean that the activity is something they enjoy in their personal lives; it often involves professional considerations, such as meeting the requirements of the scene or fulfilling the expectations of the audience.\n\nIt's also important to recognize that acting in adult films is a form of performance, and performers may separate their on-screen activities from their personal preferences and experiences. Just as with any profession, individuals in the adult industry have diverse experiences and feelings about the work they do.\n\nIf you're interested in understanding more about the experiences of adult performers, many interviews, memoirs, and documentaries provide personal insights into their lives and careers.",
